# 🏪 PlayPen House — Trial vs Premium Feature Categorization

> **Complete deep analysis** of every feature in the codebase, categorized into **Trial (Free)** and **Premium (Locked)** tiers for a subscription-based trial version.

---

## 📋 Guiding Principles

The trial version should let a store owner **explore the platform** and perform basic store operations:
- ✅ **Trial**: Add/manage products, browse the storefront, process basic orders
- 🔒 **Premium**: Advanced business tools, analytics, marketing, customer engagement, and scaling features

---

## 🗂️ COMPLETE FEATURE INVENTORY

### 1. Admin Authentication & Access

| Feature | Tier | Rationale |
|---------|------|-----------|
| Admin Login (password-protected panel) | ✅ **Trial** | Essential to access any admin functionality |
| Admin Logout | ✅ **Trial** | Basic session management |
| Admin Sidebar Navigation | ✅ **Trial** | Core UI navigation (premium tabs show lock icon) |
| Admin Navbar | ✅ **Trial** | Core UI component |
| Theme Toggle (Light/Dark) | ✅ **Trial** | Basic UI preference |

---

### 2. Admin Dashboard (`/adm/dashboard`)

| Feature | Tier | Rationale |
|---------|------|-----------|
| Basic Welcome Screen | ✅ **Trial** | Simple landing view |
| Quick Stats Cards (Products, Categories, Orders count) | ✅ **Trial** | Basic counts only |
| Revenue Analytics (Total Revenue, Monthly Revenue Charts) | 🔒 **Premium** | Advanced financial analytics |
| Timeline/Date Range Filtering (7d, 1m, 3m, custom, lifetime) | 🔒 **Premium** | Advanced analytics filtering |
| Order Status Breakdown (pie/bar chart) | 🔒 **Premium** | Advanced order analytics |
| Low Stock Alerts | 🔒 **Premium** | Inventory intelligence |
| Recent Orders Table | 🔒 **Premium** | Quick operational overview |

**Trial Dashboard**: Shows product count, category count, and a basic order count only. All charts, revenue, and alerts are blurred/locked with an "Upgrade to Premium" overlay.

