## ⚠️ Trial Version Restrictions Summary

| Restriction | Trial Limit | Premium |
|------------|:-----------:|:-------:|
| Products | Max **20** | Unlimited |
| Categories | Max **5** | Unlimited |
| Orders | Unlimited ✅ | Unlimited |
| Banners | ❌ Locked | Unlimited |
| Coupons | ❌ Locked | Unlimited |
| Customer CRM | ❌ Locked | Full Access |
| Analytics Dashboard | Basic counts only | Full charts + revenue |
| Marketing Tools | ❌ Locked | Full Access |
| Email Notifications | ❌ Locked | Full Access |
| Return Management | ❌ Locked | Full Access |

---

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This categorization ensures the trial version is **fully functional for a small store owner to explore and test** — they can add products, set up categories, and process orders. All **advanced marketing, CRM, analytics, and scaling tools** are locked behind Premium to incentivize upgrade.

> [!NOTE]
> The storefront remains mostly functional in Trial mode so customers can still shop. Only promotional widgets (banners, popups, special offers) that require premium admin features are hidden on the storefront.
